    <Paragraph>This topic provides an overview of the sample font pack containing OpenType fonts that are distributed with the Windows SDK. The sample fonts support extended OpenType features that can be used by Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF) applications.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>This topic contains the following sections.
    </Paragraph>

